當天全國的核酸檢測陽性比率為9.6%，全國的床位平均飽和率已達到95%。 鑑於嚴峻的疫情形勢，智利衛生部宣布從27日開始，首都聖地亞哥大區再次全部進入&ldquo;隔離階段&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"係唔係已經踏上咗滅國之路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8e9e5ed88c447f5d3dc17d5aecd437c9005e33","tid":2461860,"uid":291526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"超越前頂就好笑"},{"pid":"9cf70bf240877361a0cb221718aa49ea07abe3ed","tid":2461860,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/chile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Flatino%2Fchile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=7cf571ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/chile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505</a><br />\n<br />\nOn Saturday, Chile recorded its highest number of daily cases since the beginning of the pandemic, 7,084 new Covid-19 cases, breaking the single-day record of 6,938 reported in June. <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDelivering around 225,000 doses a day &mdash; mostly of the Chinese Sinovac vaccine &mdash; Chile has administered nearly 9 million doses so far, equivalent to 47 doses per 100 people, according to the University of Oxford in England. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9cf70bf240877361a0cb221718aa49ea07abe3ed","tid":2461860,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/chile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Flatino%2Fchile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=7cf571ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/chile-critical-grip-second-covid-wave-one-best-vaccination-rates-rcna505</a><br />\n<br />\nOn Saturday, Chile recorded its highest number of daily cases since the beginning of the pandemic, 7,084 new Covid-19 cases, breaking the single-day record of 6,938 reported in June. <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDelivering around 225,000 doses a day &mdash; mostly of the Chinese Sinovac vaccine &mdash; Chile has administered nearly 9 million doses so far, equivalent to 47 doses per 100 people, according to the University of Oxford in England. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}